#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Indice dei comandi"

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main &tellico; Window"
msgstr "La finestra principale di &tellico;"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each menu item is discussed below. When there is a keyboard shortcut that "
"performs a menu item function, the default shortcut is listed with the menu "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Ogni voce di menu è descritta qui sotto. Se un'azione del menu può essere "
"eseguita tramite una scorciatoia da tastiera, la lettera che l'attiva è "
"sottolineata nella corrispondente voce del menu."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Il menu File"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nuovo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>creates a new collection</action>. &tellico; supports "
"<link linkend=\"collection-types\">12 default collection types</link> along "
"with an empty user-defined custom collection. Any custom-saved collection "
"templates will also be available."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>crea una nuova collezione</action>. &tellico; "
"supporta <link linkend=\"collection-types\">12 tipi di collezioni "
"predefinite</link>, oltre a una raccolta vuota personalizzabile definita "
"dall'utente. Sarà inoltre disponibile qualsiasi modello di raccolta salvato "
"su misura."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Apri...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "This command <action>opens a &tellico; file</action>."
msgstr "Questo comando <action>apre un file di &tellico;</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open Recent</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Apri recente</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens a file</action> from a submenu that contains a "
"list of recently opened files."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>apre un file</action> selezionabile da un elenco dei "
"file aperti di recente."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Salva...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>saves the collection</action>. If the file is "
"<emphasis>Untitled</emphasis> then <guimenuitem>Save...</guimenuitem> is "
"equivalent to <guimenuitem>Save As</guimenuitem>. It is only enabled when "
"the collection has been modified."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>salva la collezione</action>. Se il file è "
"<emphasis>senza titolo</emphasis> <guimenuitem>Salva...</guimenuitem> "
"equivale a <guimenuitem>Salva come</guimenuitem>. È attivo solo quando la "
"collezione è stata modificata."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Salva come...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "This command <action>saves the collection to a new file</action>."
msgstr "Questo comando <action>salva la collezione in un nuovo file</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save As Template...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Salva come modello...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>saves the collection as a new template</action>. Only "
"the fields are saved, and the custom collection type can be created via the "
"<guimenuitem>New Collection</guimenuitem> command."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>salva la collezione come un nuovo modello</action>. "
"Vengono salvati solo i campi, mentre il tipo di collezione personalizzata "
"può essere creato col comando <guimenuitem>Nuova collezione</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stampa...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>prints the collection</action>. Printing options may be "
"set in the <interface>Configuration Dialog</interface>."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>stampa la collezione</action>. Le opzioni di stampa "
"possono essere impostate nella <interface>finestra di  configurazione</"
"interface>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print Preview</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Anteprima di stampa</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>shows a preview of the printed collection</action>."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>mostra un'anteprima della collezione stampata</"
"action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Importa</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>imports data from another file</action>. &tellico; can "
"import data from a number of <link linkend=\"importing\">other formats</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>importa dati da un altro file</action>. &tellico; può "
"importare dati da molti <link linkend=\"importing\">altri formati</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Esporta</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>exports the collection to another format</action>. "
"&tellico; can export data to a number of <link linkend=\"exporting\">other "
"formats</link>."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>esporta la collezione in un altro formato</action>. "
"&tellico; può esportare dati in diversi <link linkend=\"exporting\">altri "
"formati</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Esci</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>closes the &tellico; window</action>. If the collection "
"has unsaved changes, you will be prompted to save them before continuing."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>chiude la finestra di &tellico;</action>. Se nella "
"collezione ci sono modifiche non salvate, vi sarà chiesto di salvarle prima "
"di uscire."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr "Il menu Modifica"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Annulla</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>undoes the previous action</action>. Not all actions "
"are supported by Undo."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>annulla le azioni precedenti</action>. Non tutte le "
"azioni possono essere annullate con questo comando."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rifai</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "This command <action>reverts a previous Undo</action>."
msgstr "Questo comando <action>rifà un'azione annullata</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Taglia</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>removes the selected text</action>, if any, and "
"<action>places a copy of the removed text in the clipboard</action>."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>rimuove il testo selezionato</action> e <action>crea "
"una copia del testo rimosso negli appunti</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copia</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>copies the selected text</action>, if any, to the "
"clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>copia il testo selezionato</action>negli appunti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Incolla</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>pastes the text in the clipboard</action>, if any, into "
"the editor at the cursor position."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>incolla il testo dagli appunti</action>, se presente, "
"nell'editor alla posizione del cursore."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Seleziona tutto</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>selects all the entries</action> in the collection, in "
"the <interface>Column View</interface>."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>seleziona tutti gli elementi</action> della "
"collezione nella <interface>Vista a colonna</interface>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Deselect</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Deseleziona</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>deselects all the entries</action> in the collection."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>deseleziona tutti gli elementi</action> della "
"collezione."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Internet Search...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ricerca su Internet...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens the <interface>Internet Search Dialog</"
"interface></action> to search for and import entries from various Internet "
"sites, including <ulink url=\"http://amazon.com\">Amazon.com</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>apre la <interface>finestra Ricerca Internet</"
"interface></action> per cercare e importare elementi da vari siti Internet, "
"incluso <ulink url=\"http://amazon.com\">Amazon.com</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Advanced Filter...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Filtro avanzato...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens the <interface>Advanced Filter Dialog</"
"interface></action>."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>apre la <interface>finestra di dialogo filtro "
"avanzato</interface></action>."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Collection Menu"
msgstr "Il menu Collezione"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Entry</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Collezione</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nuovo elemento</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens the <interface>Entry Editor</interface> to edit a "
"new entry</action>."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>apre l'<interface>editor degli elementi</interface> "
"per inserirne uno nuovo</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Edit Entry</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Collezione</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Modifica elemento</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens the <interface>Entry Editor</interface> to edit "
"the selected entries</action>."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>apre l'<interface>editor degli elementi</interface> "
"sugli elementi selezionati</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Y</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Duplicate Entry</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo><keycap>&Ctrl;</keycap><keycap>Y</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Collezione</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Duplica elemento</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>copies, or duplicates, the selected entries</action> as "
"new entries in the collection."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>copia, o duplica, gli elementi selezionati</action> "
"come nuovi elementi della collezione."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Delete Entry</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo><keycap>&Ctrl;</keycap><keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Collezione</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Elimina elemento</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "This command <action>deletes the selected entries</action>."
msgstr "Questo comando <action>cancella gli elementi selezionati</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Merge Entries</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Collezione</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Fondi elementi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid "This command <action>merges the selected entries</action>."
msgstr "Questo comando <action>unisce gli elementi selezionati</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Update Entry</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Collezione</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Aggiorna elementi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu contains a list of all available data sources, and can be used to "
"automatically query the source and <action>update the selected entries</"
"action>."
msgstr ""
"Questo menu contiene una lista di tutte le fonti di dati disponibili, e può "
"essere usato per interrogarle automaticamente e <action>aggiornare gli "
"elementi selezionati</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Check-out</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Collezione</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Presta</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens a dialog box for loaning the selected entries.</"
"action>."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>apre una finestra per il prestito degli elementi "
"selezionati</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Check-in</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Collezione</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Riconsegna</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>checks-in any of the selected entries which are "
"currently on-loan</action>."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>marca come riconsegnati tutti gli elementi "
"selezionati che sono attualmente in prestito</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rename Collection</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo><keycap>&Ctrl;</keycap><keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Collezione</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rinomina collezione</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:489
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens a dialog box for renaming the collection</action>."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>apre na finestra di dialogo per rinominare la "
"collezione</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Collection Fields...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo><keycap>&Ctrl;</keycap><keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Collezione</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Campi della "
"collezione...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens the <interface>Collection Fields Dialog</"
"interface></action>."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>apre la finestra <interface>Campi della collezione</"
"interface></action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Generate Reports...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Collezione</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Genera resoconti...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens the <interface>Report Dialog</interface></action> "
"for generating reports about the collection."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>apre la <interface>finestra Resoconto</interface></"
"action> per generare resoconti sulla collezione."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliography</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Convert to Bibliography</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Collezione</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliografia</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Converti in bibliografia</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>converts a book collection to a bibliography</action> "
"by adding certain fields necessary for Bibtex export, and it is only enabled "
"when a book collection is open."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>converte una collezione di libri in una bibliografia</"
"action> aggiungendo alcuni campi necessari per l'esportazione in Bibtex, ed "
"è attivo solo quando è aperta una collezione di libri."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliography</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>String Macros...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Collezione</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliografia</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Macro di stringhe...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens a dialog box for editing the Bibtex string "
"macros</action> in the collection. It is only enabled when editing a "
"bibliography."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>apre una finestra di dialogo per modificare le macro "
"di stringhe Bibtex</action> nella collezione. È attivo solo quando è aperta "
"una bibliografia."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliography</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Check for Duplicate Keys</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Collezione</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliografia</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Cerca chiavi duplicate</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>checks for duplicate Bibtex keys</action> and can "
"filter the collection to show the entries with duplicated keys."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>cerca la chiavi duplicate di Bibtex</action> e può "
"filtrare la collezione per mostrare gli elementi con chiavi duplicate."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliography</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Copy Bibtex to Clipboard</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Collezione</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliografia</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Copia dati Bibtex negli appunti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>copies a Bibtex citation</action> to the clipboard so "
"that it can pasted in a LaTeX document."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>copia una citazione Bibtex</action> negli appunti "
"cosicché possa essere poi incollata in un documento LaTeX."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Collection</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliography</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Cite Entry in Lyx</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Collezione</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bibliografia</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Cita elemento in Lyx</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>sends a citation for the selected entries</action> to "
"the so-called <emphasis><link linkend=\"hidden-bibtex-options\">lyxpipe</"
"link></emphasis> for use in <application>LyX</application>, "
"<application>Kile</application>, or other LaTeX applications. It is only "
"enabled when editing a bibliography."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>invia una citazione per l'elemento selezionato</"
"action> alla cosiddetta <emphasis><link linkend=\"hidden-bibtex-options"
"\">lyxpipe</link></emphasis> per l'uso in <application>LyX</application>, "
"<application>Kile</application>, o altre applicazioni LaTeX. È attivo solo "
"quando è aperta una bibliografia."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:599
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings and Help Menu"
msgstr "I menu Impostazioni e Aiuto"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apart from the common &kde; Settings and Help menus described in the <ulink "
"url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html\">Menu</ulink> chapter of the &kde; "
"Fundamentals documentation &tellico; has these application specific menu "
"entries:"
msgstr ""
"Oltre ai menu comuni di &kde; Impostazioni e Aiuto, descritti nel capitolo "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html\">Menu</ulink> dei Fondamentali "
"di &kde;, &tellico; possiede le proprie voci di menu:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:609
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Group View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Impostazioni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mostra vista di gruppo</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>toggles the display of the <interface>Group View</"
"interface></action>."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>visualizza o nasconde la <interface>vista di gruppo</"
"interface></action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Entry Editor</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Impostazioni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mostra editor degli elementi</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>toggles the display of the <interface>Entry Editor</"
"interface></action>."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>visualizza o nasconde l'<interface>editor degli "
"elementi</interface></action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Group Selection</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Impostazioni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Selezione di gruppo</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>changes the field used to group the entries</action> in "
"the collection."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>cambia il campo usato per raggruppare gli elementi</"
"action> della collezione."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lock Layout</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Impostazioni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Blocca disposizione</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:655
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>locks the layout</action> such that the various "
"collection views cannot be moved. Unlocking the layout allows the user to "
"rearrange them."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>blocca la disposizione</action>, in modo che le varie "
"viste della collezione non possano più essere spostate. Lo sblocco della "
"disposizione permette all'utente la riorganizzazione."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:661
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Reset Layout</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Impostazioni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Azzera disposizione</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:668
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>resets the layout</action> to the default view, which "
"may be helpful if the various views become hidden or collapsed."
msgstr ""
"Questo comando <action>ripristina la disposizione</action> alla vista "
"predefinita. Può essere utile se la varie viste diventano nascoste o "
"collassate."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:674
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Log</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Aiuto</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mostra il registro</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the <userinput>tellico --log</userinput> option is used, this command "
"shows the diagnostic log."
msgstr ""
"Quando viene usata l'opzione <userinput>tellico --log</userinput>, questo "
"comando mostra il registro diagnostico."

